{"word":"H5227 - נֹכַח - nôkach - no'-kakh - Against","slug":"H5227","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">נֹכַח</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>nôkach"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>no'-kakh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Against"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E0;&#x05DB;&#x05D7; - no&#x0302;kach</b> - <i>no'-kakh</i><p/>From the same as <a href=\"#/H5226\">H5226</a>; properly, the <i>front</i> part; used adverbially (especially with a preposition), <i>opposite</i>, <i>in front of</i>, <i>forward</i>, <i>in behalf of: - </i>(over) against, before, direct [-ly], for, right (on)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H5226\">H5226</a>, <a href=\"#/H5228\">H5228</a>, <a href=\"#/H5229\">H5229</a>"}]}